Package: vizOmics
Title: Visualization Tools for Multi-Omics Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jiadong Mao [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3818-1981>), Yinuo Sun [aut]
Maintainer: Jiadong Mao <chiatungmao@gmail.com>
Authors@R: c(
  person("Jiadong", "Mao", , "chiatungmao@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3818-1981")),
  person("Yinuo", "Sun", , "byronsunyinuoo@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: A collection of visualization and utility functions for multi-omics 
    data analysis. Includes tools for clustering alignment, score matrix visualization
    with intelligent color detection, and interactive Sankey diagrams for comparing 
    classification results. Functions extracted and enhanced from PhiSpace package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
